fields.description:
h3.  ISMP-168 - Request: Scan To Search: Unexpected Barcode Toast Copy

On Scan/Search screen, scanning a barcode other than VN or GTIN simply shoes 'Not Found' which is not very indicative of the issue at hand.

*REPRO STEPS*
 # Scan a Location Barcode or any barcode other than GTIN/VN on Scan/Search screen
 # *NOTICE* 'Not Found' is displayed
 # *EXPECTED* "Invalid Barcode Type" for scanning invalid barcode

Test Flight - SRMS - Version 1.0 (26) August 24th, 2018

iPod Touch/Sled - 11.4.1
fields.summary: Request: Scan To Search: Unexpected Barcode Toast Copy

*REPRO STEPS*
 # Select Putaway
 # Touch both Putaways and Carton Putaway at the same time

issuetype.name: Story

issuetype.description: A problem which impairs or prevents the functions of the product.
issuetype.name: Bug

fields.description:
When user putaway single item, confirmation message is: Putaway 1 Items which is misleading user to believe they might have putaway multiple items.

Steps to Reproduce:

1- Navigate to Putaway>>>Putaways screen

2- Scan a single item barcode

3- Scan the location barcode

4- Observe the putaway confirmation message "Putaway 1 Items" 

*Expected Result*: Confirmation message should be "Putaway 1 Item"

*Actual Result:* Confirmation message is : Putaway 1 Items"
fields.summary: Putaway confirmation message mislead users (putaway 1 items)
